	<title>Reader: status bar glitch after viewing photo</title>
	<description>
		<paragraph id="1">
			<sentence id="1.1">When returning to the reader after viewing an image in the full-screen photo viewer, there's sometimes a graphical glitch in the status bar.</sentence>
			<sentence id="1.2">I'm pretty sure this is [an Android bug](https://code.google.com/p/android/issues/detail?id=81832) which has since been fixed, but I recall a similar bug elsewhere that was resolved by changing an activity's background from a `@color` to an actual `@drawable`.</sentence>
		</paragraph>
		<paragraph id="2">
			<sentence id="2.1">!</sentence>
			<sentence id="2.2">[screenshot_2015-04-24-07-16-22](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/3903757/7315263/db20f77a-ea39-11e4-8f19-917b2624fe9f.png)</sentence>
